{"id": "1379154410470641684", "channel_id": "1379154410470641684", "type": 0, "author_id": "812757006066515969", "author_name": "dodododo4444", "author_bot": false, "content": "\"You have reached the maximum number of character creations\"\n\nWhat can I do? I can't even login to existing account", "timestamp": "2025-06-02T17:47:14.906000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-06-02T18:10:29.812000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1379154410621505536", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 180132, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1379154410470641684/1379154410621505536/image.png?ex=69ff7322&is=69fe21a2&hm=784bf10186157761901e52fa9d68a1ae41bb12a5430a8fd9ab44d4bc724e4705&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1379154410470641684", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Cannot login \"You have reached the maximum number of character creations\"", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1378984085766013028", "channel_id": "1378984085766013028", "type": 0, "author_id": "1154601435141509192", "author_name": "jormiejormungandr", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hello. Can you please add this Ryker emote here on discord? <:please:1356053110375714817>", "timestamp": "2025-06-02T06:30:26.332000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-06-02T06:30:45.393000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1378984085988573225", "filename": "PLEAsE_RKYER_BEG.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 21032, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1378984085766013028/1378984085988573225/PLEAsE_RKYER_BEG.jpg?ex=6a00cec2&is=69ff7d42&hm=d0f2fc0bf5f3b0705adfe24b5c8cf48bf10887e21adf8b67127858d467927e40&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1378984085766013028", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Emote", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1379040722942169209", "channel_id": "1379040722942169209", "type": 0, "author_id": "735137568307282011", "author_name": "reya.li", "author_bot": false, "content": "I was farming the Bleak Tide event yesterday for about 70 minutes, and this particular stage has the Ch. 5/6 moving ship deck and shifting pink skies background. \n\nMy sister and I both suffer from a photosensitive seizure condition - I did not have one as a result of the game, to be clear, however, it did make me extremely nauseous and cause my left eye to dilate and unfocus a lot until the next day. Obviously I should've stopped playing sooner, but I kind of zoned out into my gameplay.\n\nIt would be really nice if there was an option to turn off the few animated and shifting backgrounds there are in the game and change them to a still image/PNG. This would help many people's visual comfort and potentially some people's health when playing for a long time like this. It could improve game performance for older phones/PCs as well. \n\nHope you'll consider implementing this setting in the future, thank you.\n\nDeepSeek <:huh2:1356083942901420033> \n我昨天花了約70分鐘刷『蒼潮』活動關卡，其中某一關的背景是第5/6章那種移動的船甲板和變幻的粉紅色天空。\n\n我和妹妹都有光敏性癲癇的問題——先聲明，我並沒有因此發作，但這個背景確實讓我感到極度噁心，左眼瞳孔持續放大且無法對焦，直到隔天才恢復。當然，我應該早點停下來，但玩著玩著就有點恍神了。\n\n如果能提供選項，關閉遊戲中少數動態變換的背景，改為靜態圖片/PNG，那就太好了。這不僅能提升許多玩家的視覺舒適度，甚至對部分長時間遊玩的人的健康也有幫助，同時可能改善舊手機/電腦的遊戲性能。\n\n希望未來能考慮加入這個設定，謝謝。", "timestamp": "2025-06-02T10:15:29.687000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-06-02T10:16:06.354000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😲", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "thumbsup", "emoji_id": "1356086340298473574", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1379040723231309925", "filename": "rkglgr.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 344872, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1379040722942169209/1379040723231309925/rkglgr.png?ex=6a005ac1&is=69ff0941&hm=a5beb0072dce44fc8fdd54433b1cb60a647d7979aaf34f65dd35b48baee4f732&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1379040722942169209", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Please make animated backgrounds be able to be turned off. 請提供關閉動畫背景的選項。", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
